OL,6,FA man from Hove who committed more
OL,7,Fthan 70 sexual offences against young
OL,8,Fpeople over more than two decades has
OL,9,Fbeen sentenced to a total of 22 years,
OL,10,F16 of which will be spent in prison.
OL,12,FIan Silvester, 60, used his roles as a
OL,13,Fscout leader, children's nurse, St
OL,14,FJohn Ambulance worker, diving
OL,15,Finstructor, first aid trainer and
OL,16,Fbabysitter to attack 19 children and
OL,17,Fyoung men on more than 200 occasions
OL,18,Fbetween 1986 and 2011. Some were as
OL,19,Fyoung as seven years old.
